---
title: Mexican Beef & Sweetcorn Quesadillas with Cheddar Cheese & Sour Cream | Serves 2
description: These easy beef quesadillas cook all in one pan - perfect for a no fuss lunch. Add the bold Mexican flavours you know and
love, plus a pop of bright corn and rich sour cream and these will quickly be your new midday favourites.
